- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also likely as the paper discusses the development of an open source Android application.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper discusses self-compilation techniques used in the application.
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the use of smartphones as a means of storing and transferring data.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also less likely but possible as the paper discusses the use of a tool to protect user data in various situations.
